1.101 Thu 16 Oct 2014
	- Default HSTS maxage now 26 weeks instead of 6
	  (Qualys SSL Labs recommend at least 180 days)

1.100 Thu 15 May 2014
	- Support for HTTP Strict Transport Security (enabled by default)

